overview: Neptune's Empire: Second Life ambience (2011) by Jon Rafman  Upon whose influence Neptune's empire stands  Was sick almost to doomsday with eclipse:  And even the like precurse of fierce events,  As harbingers preceding still the fates  And prologue to the omen coming on,  Have heaven and earth together demonstrated  Unto our climatures and countrymen.--  But soft, behold! lo, where it comes again!
title: Neptune’s Empire: Second Life ambience
